हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: When Peng yang discovers his wife in another man's arms, his world shatters. Reeling from betrayal, he demands a divorce and drowns his sorrows in alcohol—only to be stabbed by his furious mother-in-law, who blames him for everything. As his vision fades, he believes his story is over… But fate has other plans. Pengyang wakes up in 1994, decades before the heartbreak, betrayal, and bloodshed. Armed with knowledge of the future and a second chance at life, can he rewrite his destiny? Will he seek revenge—or redemption? Watch "Back to 1994" now!
